603
00:40:02.569 --> 00:40:04.070
<i>This is our home.</i>

604
00:40:04.071 --> 00:40:05.821
<i>We are the people of Mars.</i>

605
00:40:05.822 --> 00:40:07.324
<i>We speak as one.</i>

606
00:40:10.869 --> 00:40:13.372
