655
00:46:08.227 --> 00:46:10.102
<i>You will receive no new food.</i>

656
00:46:10.103 --> 00:46:16.860
{\an8}<i>You will receive no new medication.
You will receive no support from Earth.</i>

657
00:46:17.819 --> 00:46:22.241
